# UDM deployment targets for deploy-to-udms.sh
#
# Format: host_or_ip [bind_ip]
# - host_or_ip: Target UDM hostname or IP address (required)
# - bind_ip: Source IP for SCP/SSH BindAddress (optional; if omitted, uses LOCAL_UDM_IP from vpn-monitor.conf)
#
# Lines starting with # or empty are ignored.
# Username and password are prompted for each UDM.
#
# Copy to deploy-udms.conf (in repo/install root) and add your UDMs:
#   cp scripts/deploy-udms.conf.example deploy-udms.conf
#
# Example entries:
# 192.168.1.100
# 192.168.1.101 192.168.50.1
# vpn-gateway.example.com
